Description_lang: Increases your maximum health by an additional $s1% and your damage taken is reduced by an additional $s2% while Fortifying Brew is active.

description_blz.en_US: Increases your maximum health by an additional 10% and your damage taken is reduced by an additional 10% while Fortifying Brew is active.
description_blz.es_MX: Aumenta tu salud máxima un 10% adicional y el daño recibido se reduce un 10% más mientras Brebaje reconstituyente esté activo.
description_blz.pt_BR: Aumenta em mais 10% seu máximo de pontos de vida, e o dano recebido é reduzido em mais 10% enquanto Cerveja Fortificante estiver ativa.
description_blz.de_DE: Erhöht Eure maximale Gesundheit zusätzlich um 10%, und der von Euch erlittene Schaden wird um zusätzliche 10% verringert, solange 'Stärkendes Gebräu' aktiv ist.
description_blz.en_GB: Increases your maximum health by an additional 10% and your damage taken is reduced by an additional 10% while Fortifying Brew is active.
description_blz.es_ES: Aumenta un 10% más tu salud máxima, y tu daño recibido se reduce un 10% más mientras Brebaje reconstituyente está activo.
description_blz.fr_FR: Augmente votre maximum de points de vie de 10 % supplémentaires et réduit les dégâts subis de 10 % supplémentaires tant que Boisson fortifiante est active.
description_blz.it_IT: Aumenta la salute massima del 10% e riduce i danni subiti del 10% aggiuntivo quando Birra Fortificante è attiva.
description_blz.ru_RU: "Укрепляющий отвар" увеличивает максимальный запас здоровья еще на 10% и уменьшает получаемый урон еще на 10%.
description_blz.ko_KR: 강화주가 활성화된 동안 최대 생명력이 추가로 10%만큼 증가하고 받는 피해는 10%만큼 감소합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 在石形絕釀作用期間，你的生命力上限額外提高10%，受到的傷害額外降低10%。
description_blz.zh_CN: 壮胆酒激活时，你的最大生命值额外提高10%，受到的伤害额外降低10%。
